    @EventNotifier
public class ResponseReceiveEventNotifier
extends EventNotifierBase<org.apache.camel.management.event.ExchangeSentEvent>
    Listens to response receive (event = ExchangeSentEvent). If endpoint URI is successfully filtered and saving is enabled then response is saved to DB.
